CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 25, 1957, pg. A11 reads: "The Winnah! - Joe Sanford succeeded in this mighty-man effort and KO'd Arnie Sowell in the Omega Psi Phi and Kappa Nu joint production of "One Punch Will Tell." The comic skit was the contribution of the two fraternities during the annual Pitt Carnival, held recently.  Pictured with Arnie and Joe are a few of the members who helped make the show one of the carnival's hits. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Omega Psi Phi and Kappa Nu fraternity members including Arnold "Arnie" Sowell lying down and Joe Sanford with boxing gloves raised, posed outdoors in front of wall inscribed "One Punch Will Tell" during University of Pittsburgh Carnival, another version
